1
00:00:01,250 --> 00:00:03,920
Yeon Sil.
 [Episode 51]

2
00:00:06,220 --> 00:00:11,590
Please forgive me once.

3
00:00:14,700 --> 00:00:20,800
Let me go to her.

4
00:00:22,860 --> 00:00:26,480
While she's getting her surgery,

5
00:00:26,480 --> 00:00:30,830
please allow me to be with her.

6
00:00:30,830 --> 00:00:34,200
Please.

7
00:00:34,210 --> 00:00:37,710
I beg you.

8
00:00:37,750 --> 00:00:43,460
Are you saying...

9
00:00:43,460 --> 00:00:47,330
Are you saying you want to abandon me?

10
00:00:47,330 --> 00:00:52,560
Are you breaking up with me?

11
00:00:59,530 --> 00:01:01,750
Why would I break up with you?

12
00:01:01,750 --> 00:01:04,950
That's not what I mean.

13
00:01:04,950 --> 00:01:09,340
We can't leave her to die like that.

14
00:01:09,340 --> 00:01:12,400
We have to save her first.

15
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:16,290
If I let her go like this,

16
00:01:16,290 --> 00:01:20,090
I will regret it for the rest of my life.

17
00:01:20,090 --> 00:01:22,910
Honey.

18
00:01:22,910 --> 00:01:26,030
Please let it go, just once.

19
00:01:26,030 --> 00:01:28,050
Please.

20
00:01:28,050 --> 00:01:32,250
Please don't make it harder for her.

21
00:01:33,660 --> 00:01:35,940
I...

22
00:01:35,960 --> 00:01:39,130
I'm not saying I'll do something with her.

23
00:01:39,130 --> 00:01:42,170
I just want to keep her alive and send her to the US.

24
00:01:42,170 --> 00:01:44,200
That's all I want.

25
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:47,850
So, for the sake of Dan Dan, please.

26
00:01:47,850 --> 00:01:52,890
I beg you, Honey.

27
00:01:54,540 --> 00:01:56,530
If you want to go, go.

28
00:01:56,530 --> 00:01:59,810
But sign the divorce papers before you go.

29
00:01:59,810 --> 00:02:03,430
You can go after breaking up with me.

30
00:02:03,430 --> 00:02:04,840
What?

31
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:07,250
If you want to live with her that much,

32
00:02:07,250 --> 00:02:10,710
write a paper that you'll divorce me first!

33
00:02:10,710 --> 00:02:14,430
How can you do this to me? How!

34
00:02:14,430 --> 00:02:17,070
Think about it from my position.

35
00:02:17,070 --> 00:02:20,580
Think about it from my position!

36
00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:27,020
Father. Aren't you going too overboard?

37
00:02:27,020 --> 00:02:29,700
How can you say such things to Mom?

38
00:02:29,700 --> 00:02:32,950
You can't be acting like this toward Mom!

39
00:02:32,950 --> 00:02:35,450
Dae Beom, please.

40
00:02:35,450 --> 00:02:39,650
Please stay out of it.

41
00:02:43,690 --> 00:02:48,960
Okay, go. Go!

42
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:52,860
I don't need you anymore.

43
00:02:52,860 --> 00:02:57,520
What is she to you to be acting like this to me?

44
00:02:57,520 --> 00:03:00,740
How can you do this to me!

45
00:03:00,740 --> 00:03:04,990
How?

46
00:03:04,990 --> 00:03:07,840
- Mom. Mom.
- Dae Beom!

47
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:10,560
Don't cry, Mom.

48
00:03:12,390 --> 00:03:15,190
How can he do this to me?

49
00:03:15,190 --> 00:03:18,690
How? How?

50
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:28,200
Dad.

51
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:31,410
Yes, Dan Dan.

52
00:03:31,410 --> 00:03:33,450
What's wrong with you?

53
00:03:33,450 --> 00:03:37,920
I can't understand why you are doing this. So I came to ask you.

54
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:40,260
How can you say those things to Mom?

55
00:03:40,260 --> 00:03:43,190
Do you think that makes sense?

56
00:03:43,190 --> 00:03:46,040
Dan Dan.

57
00:03:46,040 --> 00:03:48,860
CEO Anna Kim,

58
00:03:48,860 --> 00:03:51,760
she's very sick.

59
00:03:51,790 --> 00:03:55,490
But she has no one by her side.

60
00:03:55,490 --> 00:04:00,120
How can she endure and survive such a scary disease alone? That's why.

61
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:07,530
So I'm saying, what's your relationship with her to say it like that?

62
00:04:07,530 --> 00:04:13,610
She's the mother who gave birth to you, Dan Dan.

63
00:04:15,090 --> 00:04:17,170
Dad.

64
00:04:17,170 --> 00:04:22,620
You hated her so much, have you forgotten?

65
00:04:22,650 --> 00:04:25,170
Okay, I see how that could happen.

66
00:04:25,170 --> 00:04:28,060
You could forgive her. But...

67
00:04:28,060 --> 00:04:30,710
You can't be like that toward Mom.

68
00:04:30,710 --> 00:04:33,050
She's the one who's been by your side all this time.

69
00:04:33,050 --> 00:04:38,840
But how can you say such ruthless things to Mom?

70
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:41,200
If you want to go to CEO Anna,

71
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:45,980
divorce my mom as she requested.

72
00:04:48,370 --> 00:04:51,560
Okay.

73
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:54,310
I understand.

74
00:04:54,310 --> 00:04:57,150
I'm sorry.

75
00:04:57,150 --> 00:04:59,830
I know I've done wrong.

76
00:04:59,830 --> 00:05:02,370
If you know, then go and apologize to Mom.

77
00:05:02,370 --> 00:05:05,780
Ask her for forgiveness. Okay?

78
00:05:05,780 --> 00:05:07,730
Okay.

79
00:05:09,090 --> 00:05:12,050
But Dan Dan.

80
00:05:12,050 --> 00:05:16,720
CEO Anna Kim has to get surgery soon.

81
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:22,680
If something goes wrong while she's alone, I thought it might hurt your feelings.

82
00:05:22,690 --> 00:05:25,800
What's it to us if she dies or not?

83
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:29,240
And why would I be hurt?

84
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:10,570
Honey.

85
00:06:11,890 --> 00:06:14,960
I've done wrong.

86
00:06:14,960 --> 00:06:18,590
I'm really sorry.

87
00:06:18,590 --> 00:06:23,800
I must have lost my senses.

88
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:30,470
I will not say such a thing again.

89
00:06:30,470 --> 00:06:36,740
I will not pay attention to whether she lives or dies from now on.

90
00:06:36,740 --> 00:06:40,900
So please don't be upset anymore.

91
00:06:55,300 --> 00:06:57,750
I've heard about it.

92
00:06:59,630 --> 00:07:02,810
That you've been very sick.

93
00:07:02,810 --> 00:07:05,490
But I didn't know.

94
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:09,800
If there is anything I can help you with,

95
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:12,030
please tell me anything.

96
00:07:12,030 --> 00:07:14,230
It's okay.

97
00:07:14,230 --> 00:07:17,420
No one can help me.

98
00:07:17,420 --> 00:07:21,830
This is something I have to endure on my own.

99
00:07:21,830 --> 00:07:23,960
Let's not talk about it.

100
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:28,310
I have so much to tell you.

101
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:29,820
Really?

102
00:07:29,820 --> 00:07:36,650
I've been feeling terribly sorry toward you.

103
00:07:38,730 --> 00:07:44,340
I've wanted to say this for so long, and finally, here I am.

104
00:07:44,340 --> 00:07:47,280
You don't have to.

105
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:51,050
Don't worry about it, I'm fine.

106
00:07:53,060 --> 00:07:57,380
You've always been a great support to me.

107
00:07:57,380 --> 00:08:02,610
Whenever I came to Korea, you welcomed me like family.

108
00:08:02,610 --> 00:08:04,610
So I always said in words

109
00:08:04,610 --> 00:08:09,630
that we are a family, you are my brother.

110
00:08:09,630 --> 00:08:12,940
But I've hurt you a lot.

111
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:18,240
Noona.

112
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:24,200
It wasn't because I didn't like you.

113
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:28,640
Nor because you did something wrong.

114
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:36,790
It was all because my guilt and regret of abandoning Dan Dan were too big.

115
00:08:36,790 --> 00:08:39,520
I wanted to take her with me.

116
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:43,460
And give her everything I couldn't do until now.

117
00:08:43,460 --> 00:08:48,250
I was being greedy and acted wrong again.

118
00:08:48,250 --> 00:08:54,830
I didn't think of you but only Dan Dan.

119
00:08:54,830 --> 00:09:02,600
And I also thought my Dan Dan was too young to be with you.

120
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:05,670
And precious to give her to you.

121
00:09:05,670 --> 00:09:09,530
I didn't think of your feelings at all.

122
00:09:11,530 --> 00:09:14,640
I'm sorry, Young Gook.

123
00:09:16,580 --> 00:09:18,840
Noona.

124
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:21,600
You don't have to say all that.

125
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:24,140
I'm all right.

126
00:09:29,950 --> 00:09:31,770
Young Gook.

127
00:09:31,770 --> 00:09:39,090
You still do have feelings for my Dan Dan, don't you?

128
00:09:39,090 --> 00:09:41,710
I do.

129
00:09:41,760 --> 00:09:44,670
We are seeing each other again.

130
00:09:44,730 --> 00:09:47,960
We will not break up again.

131
00:09:50,390 --> 00:09:55,750
Yes, I'm glad it's you who my Dan Dan loves.

132
00:09:55,750 --> 00:10:01,950
I know you'll be able to make her happy.

133
00:10:04,290 --> 00:10:06,700
Young Gook.

134
00:10:08,700 --> 00:10:11,660
Please take good care of her.

135
00:10:11,660 --> 00:10:15,690
Please make my Dan Dan happy.

136
00:10:23,020 --> 00:10:26,600
Don't worry about Ms. Park.

137
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:30,820
You have to overcome this.

138
00:10:30,820 --> 00:10:37,670
And watch Ms. Park and me being happy together.

139
00:10:37,670 --> 00:10:40,150
Yes.

140
00:10:40,180 --> 00:10:43,590
Yes, I will.

141
00:10:43,590 --> 00:10:46,630
Thank you, Young Gook.

142
00:10:56,640 --> 00:11:00,690
Chairman, where are we going today?

143
00:11:00,690 --> 00:11:04,050
- We are going for lunch.
- Lunch?

144
00:11:04,050 --> 00:11:07,270
There is a really good bulgogi restaurant nearby.

145
00:11:07,270 --> 00:11:09,740
I know you like bulgogi.

146
00:11:09,740 --> 00:11:13,450
But why do you look so serious when we are going for lunch?

147
00:11:13,450 --> 00:11:16,580
You look like you are going on a battle.

148
00:11:16,580 --> 00:11:18,430
- Do I?
- Yes.

149
00:11:18,430 --> 00:11:22,280
You look like someone with a big task ahead.

150
00:11:40,160 --> 00:11:44,470
Ms. Park, Ji Young Noona seemed like she wanted to see you.

151
00:11:44,470 --> 00:11:47,410
But she seemed to have trouble initiating.

152
00:11:47,410 --> 00:11:50,840
So I arranged this today.

153
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:53,210
I'm sorry for not telling you first.

154
00:11:53,210 --> 00:12:00,310
But don't you also want to see Ji Young Noona as well?

155
00:12:02,300 --> 00:12:03,890
Chairman.

156
00:12:03,890 --> 00:12:08,610
Just think of it as having lunch together.

157
00:12:18,870 --> 00:12:21,060
Young Gook.

158
00:12:21,060 --> 00:12:23,880
Dan Dan.

159
00:12:23,880 --> 00:12:26,790
Noona, I wanted to have lunch with you.

160
00:12:26,790 --> 00:12:29,500
But I have to leave due to an urgent matter.

161
00:12:29,500 --> 00:12:33,900
Why don't you two eat together?

162
00:12:33,900 --> 00:12:36,590
Ms. Park, please sit.

163
00:12:41,610 --> 00:12:45,230
I've already ordered everything and paid for it.

164
00:12:45,230 --> 00:12:48,910
So please enjoy and eat as much as you want.

165
00:12:48,910 --> 00:12:51,900
Noona. I will get going.

166
00:12:59,910 --> 00:13:04,870
Dan Dan, please don't misunderstand.

167
00:13:04,870 --> 00:13:07,420
I didn't ask him to do this.

168
00:13:07,420 --> 00:13:10,430
Young Gook asked me to have lunch together.

169
00:13:10,430 --> 00:13:15,150
So I thought it would be just two of us and didn't know you would come.

170
00:13:15,150 --> 00:13:17,930
Please don't misunderstand.

171
00:13:17,930 --> 00:13:20,260
Please sit.

172
00:13:36,030 --> 00:13:40,300
Have you been well?

173
00:13:40,300 --> 00:13:42,320
Yes.

174
00:13:50,790 --> 00:13:55,930
I would have paid more attention if I knew I would see you.

175
00:13:55,930 --> 00:13:59,140
I look terrible, don't I?

176
00:13:59,140 --> 00:14:04,690
Young Gook should've said something.

177
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:22,630
Here.

178
00:14:22,630 --> 00:14:26,850
Eat as much as you want. You like bulgogi.

179
00:14:36,880 --> 00:14:41,960
Please eat. You have to eat well.

180
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:45,680
Okay, thank you. Let's eat.

181
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:08,030
Please take care. Goodbye.

182
00:15:09,470 --> 00:15:12,650
Wait, Dan Dan.

183
00:15:16,830 --> 00:15:20,760
Can we go for coffee together?

184
00:15:20,760 --> 00:15:23,660
Are you okay to drink coffee?

185
00:15:23,660 --> 00:15:27,100
I heard you are getting surgery next week.

186
00:15:28,900 --> 00:15:34,700
Well, I just thought...

187
00:15:34,700 --> 00:15:39,240
I just want to sit in front of you, at least.

188
00:15:41,460 --> 00:15:46,110
I just want to see your face for a little longer.

189
00:15:55,250 --> 00:15:58,750
When you want to be with me this much,

190
00:15:58,750 --> 00:16:03,310
and you want to see my face a little longer,

191
00:16:03,310 --> 00:16:06,280
why?

192
00:16:06,280 --> 00:16:10,180
Why did you deceive me all this time?

193
00:16:10,180 --> 00:16:13,350
If you had told me who you were from the beginning.

194
00:16:13,350 --> 00:16:19,950
Then we could have spent more time together.

195
00:16:21,720 --> 00:16:27,550
After all this time, what do you want me to do?

196
00:16:29,800 --> 00:16:34,700
Why do you hurt my heart this bad? Why?

197
00:16:36,650 --> 00:16:39,250
Dan Dan.

198
00:16:39,250 --> 00:16:40,820
Don't cry.

199
00:16:40,820 --> 00:16:44,870
I'm sorry, Dan Dan.

200
00:16:46,720 --> 00:16:50,080
Dan Dan...

201
00:16:50,080 --> 00:16:54,150
Mom... Mom, I'm sorry.

202
00:16:54,150 --> 00:16:57,970
Mom. Mom, I'm sorry.

203
00:16:57,970 --> 00:17:01,330
I'm sorry. I'm sorry, Mom.

204
00:17:01,330 --> 00:17:05,450
- Mom.
- No, I'm the one who's sorry.

205
00:17:05,450 --> 00:17:08,790
Mom, I'm so sorry.

206
00:17:08,790 --> 00:17:12,540
Please don't be sick. Please don't die, Mom.

207
00:17:12,540 --> 00:17:17,210
Mom, I'm so sorry.

208
00:17:17,210 --> 00:17:19,570
Mom.

209
00:17:25,920 --> 00:17:29,280
Joon Oh, what are you doing?

210
00:17:29,280 --> 00:17:35,290
You are not selling your major's books, are you?

211
00:17:35,300 --> 00:17:39,510
Are you selling all these books because I cut off your allowances?

212
00:17:39,510 --> 00:17:42,670
No, I'm not.

213
00:17:42,670 --> 00:17:45,730
I'm going back to school.

214
00:17:45,730 --> 00:17:49,830
Oh my, Joon Oh, my son!

215
00:17:49,830 --> 00:17:52,410
My son.

216
00:17:52,410 --> 00:17:57,320
My son is finally listening to me!

217
00:17:57,320 --> 00:18:02,180
Please stop. I'm not a child.

218
00:18:02,180 --> 00:18:04,120
Mi Rim said I should go back to school.

219
00:18:04,120 --> 00:18:06,380
That's why.

220
00:18:06,380 --> 00:18:08,090
What?

221
00:18:08,090 --> 00:18:10,410
What did you say?

222
00:18:10,410 --> 00:18:13,440
You are going back to school because Mi Rim told you to?

223
00:18:13,440 --> 00:18:19,550
Yes. Mi Rim said I would make a great doctor.

224
00:18:19,550 --> 00:18:21,590
So I decided to start again.

225
00:18:21,590 --> 00:18:24,590
Oh my, you crazy punk.

226
00:18:24,590 --> 00:18:26,620
What are you saying?

227
00:18:26,620 --> 00:18:29,420
I've fed you, clothed you, provided lodging.

228
00:18:29,420 --> 00:18:31,800
And I paid for your school and allowances.

229
00:18:31,800 --> 00:18:38,180
When I, the mother who gave my life to you, asked you to go back to school, you didn't listen at all. But what?

230
00:18:38,180 --> 00:18:40,640
"Mi Rim said I should go back to school?"

231
00:18:40,640 --> 00:18:43,030
Are you really going to be like this?

232
00:18:43,030 --> 00:18:46,780
Are you going to keep dating her?

233
00:18:46,780 --> 00:18:51,640
Yes, I will never break up with Mi Rim.

234
00:18:51,640 --> 00:18:55,730
Fine. Let's see how that goes.

235
00:18:55,730 --> 00:18:59,440
Okay, let's sever our relationship as mother and son.

236
00:18:59,440 --> 00:19:01,930
I will never accept her.

237
00:19:01,930 --> 00:19:05,890
Mom. Are you being serious?

238
00:19:05,890 --> 00:19:08,360
Then I will never see you again.

239
00:19:08,360 --> 00:19:10,440
I will really end our relationship.

240
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:13,280
You don't have to take it that seriously...

241
00:19:13,280 --> 00:19:17,150
So please don't speak like that again.

242
00:19:18,600 --> 00:19:21,340
I'll be back later.

243
00:19:24,530 --> 00:19:27,470
What was that?

244
00:19:27,470 --> 00:19:34,000
That terrible boy is a traitor. A traitor.

245
00:19:41,170 --> 00:19:43,890
You and my Joon Oh's relationship,

246
00:19:43,890 --> 00:19:47,870
fine, I'll approve it.

247
00:19:47,870 --> 00:19:49,880
Really?

248
00:19:49,880 --> 00:19:54,990
I heard that Joon Oh going back to school is all thanks to you.

249
00:19:54,990 --> 00:19:58,780
So how can I blindly disapprove of you two?

250
00:19:58,780 --> 00:20:01,270
You made my wish come true.

251
00:20:01,270 --> 00:20:04,350
I'm grateful for that.

252
00:20:04,350 --> 00:20:06,210
Thank you.

253
00:20:06,210 --> 00:20:08,650
But it's not just because of me.

254
00:20:08,650 --> 00:20:11,530
Joon Oh decided for himself.

255
00:20:11,530 --> 00:20:15,350
Anyway, if you two are serious about each other,

256
00:20:15,350 --> 00:20:19,170
I'll buy an apartment near Joon Oh's school.

257
00:20:19,170 --> 00:20:24,290
So can you move in there and look after my Joon Oh?

258
00:20:24,290 --> 00:20:26,200
Pardon?

259
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:29,870
What do you mean by that?

260
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:33,090
It's not like we are getting married right now.

261
00:20:33,090 --> 00:20:36,930
There is no reason for me to move down there and look after Joon Oh.

262
00:20:36,930 --> 00:20:39,380
I don't like that idea.

263
00:20:39,380 --> 00:20:42,190
What? You don't like it?

264
00:20:42,190 --> 00:20:46,510
Haven't you been living together?

265
00:20:46,510 --> 00:20:49,070
All this time?

266
00:20:49,070 --> 00:20:53,890
Doesn't that mean you are planning to marry each other?

267
00:20:53,890 --> 00:20:56,470
Even so, we are just seeing each other.

268
00:20:56,470 --> 00:20:59,770
We've never talked about marriage.

269
00:20:59,770 --> 00:21:04,360
And I have a dream of my own.

270
00:21:04,360 --> 00:21:09,010
Now that I got the certificate, I need to build my career working in a hair salon.

271
00:21:09,010 --> 00:21:12,730
I can't throw away my dream just to support Joon Oh.

272
00:21:12,730 --> 00:21:14,190
What is it then?

273
00:21:14,190 --> 00:21:17,900
Are you going to break up when Joon Oh goes back to school?

274
00:21:17,900 --> 00:21:23,940
No, we will see each other once in a week or so, as the time allows.

275
00:21:23,940 --> 00:21:26,880
That makes no sense.

276
00:21:28,490 --> 00:21:33,210
Mi Rim, I'll open a hair salon for you.

277
00:21:33,210 --> 00:21:36,350
If your dream is to become a hairdresser.

278
00:21:37,800 --> 00:21:40,930
No, that's not right.

279
00:21:40,930 --> 00:21:44,900
What? That's not it, either?

280
00:21:44,900 --> 00:21:47,440
I'm a beginner with a lot to learn.

281
00:21:47,440 --> 00:21:51,430
How can I open a salon without experience or qualification?

282
00:21:51,430 --> 00:21:59,620
And my plan is to work under great hair designers and open my salon with my own efforts.

283
00:21:59,620 --> 00:22:04,060
I'll ask for help if I need it in the future.

284
00:22:09,590 --> 00:22:14,720
She's stubborn for someone who has nothing.

285
00:22:14,720 --> 00:22:19,130
Actually, she's right.

286
00:22:19,130 --> 00:22:22,040
Kids these days are better than me.

287
00:22:22,040 --> 00:22:26,740
That Mi Rim has it together.

288
00:22:30,180 --> 00:22:31,820
I don't know this number.

289
00:22:31,820 --> 00:22:34,030
Who could it be?

290
00:22:35,890 --> 00:22:37,980
Hello?

291
00:22:39,440 --> 00:22:43,100
Gi Ja, aren't you in jail?

292
00:22:43,100 --> 00:22:46,110
Can you make calls from jail?

293
00:22:48,320 --> 00:22:52,050
You look great.

294
00:22:52,050 --> 00:22:56,710
Maybe because I'm sleeping well.

295
00:22:56,710 --> 00:23:00,140
I've been sleeping well since I've come here.

296
00:23:01,480 --> 00:23:05,010
I feel more peaceful, if nothing else.

297
00:23:05,010 --> 00:23:09,020
But, Mi Sook.

298
00:23:09,020 --> 00:23:12,790
I can't get hold of my Sarah.

299
00:23:12,790 --> 00:23:16,350
She doesn't come to see me.

300
00:23:16,350 --> 00:23:20,100
Do you know her whereabouts, by chance?

301
00:23:20,100 --> 00:23:25,820
Did you call me here because of Sarah?

302
00:23:25,820 --> 00:23:28,690
Yes, Mi Sook.

303
00:23:28,690 --> 00:23:34,650
Can you find my Sarah? Where is she, and how she's doing?

304
00:23:34,650 --> 00:23:40,260
I don't know if she's alive or dead.

305
00:23:40,260 --> 00:23:43,110
I'm worrying to death about her.

306
00:23:43,110 --> 00:23:47,650
Gi Ja, how can I find out where Sarah is?

307
00:23:47,650 --> 00:23:51,500
It's been a long time since she left my house.

308
00:23:51,500 --> 00:23:53,370
Mi Sook.

309
00:23:53,370 --> 00:23:56,030
Nothing would've happened to my Sarah, right?

310
00:23:56,030 --> 00:24:00,310
Lee Gi Ja. If you wanted to live without any trouble in your life,

311
00:24:00,310 --> 00:24:05,020
you and your daughter should've not done such horrible things.

312
00:24:05,020 --> 00:24:08,290
Don't you agree?

313
00:24:08,330 --> 00:24:14,110
To be honest, I didn't want to come here despite your begging.

314
00:24:14,110 --> 00:24:17,990
But I came here for the last time since we've been friends for a long time.

315
00:24:17,990 --> 00:24:23,450
So please, do not contact me ever again.

316
00:24:23,450 --> 00:24:28,840
I would like to end our relationship right here.

317
00:24:28,840 --> 00:24:33,410
I'm here to say that to you.

318
00:24:33,410 --> 00:24:37,020
- Mi Sook...
- Oh, that's right.

319
00:24:37,020 --> 00:24:42,240
I put some money in for you.

320
00:24:42,240 --> 00:24:44,920
I will go now.

321
00:25:07,220 --> 00:25:09,390
To make it easier for you to eat.

322
00:25:09,390 --> 00:25:13,640
I picked out the meat for you.

323
00:25:13,640 --> 00:25:18,860
Eat with the hot broth.

324
00:25:18,860 --> 00:25:21,790
Ajussi...

325
00:25:25,460 --> 00:25:29,950
You have to eat everything well for the baby's health.

326
00:25:33,220 --> 00:25:35,650
Please eat.

327
00:25:35,650 --> 00:25:41,120
You know the potato is the highlight of the bone soup.

328
00:25:41,120 --> 00:25:45,230
Crush the potato and eat it with rice.

329
00:26:07,560 --> 00:26:09,330
Isn't it good?

330
00:26:09,330 --> 00:26:12,930
Yes, it's good.

331
00:26:14,610 --> 00:26:17,310
I knew you would like it.

332
00:26:17,310 --> 00:26:24,820
The reason is, this is what my mom liked eating when she was pregnant with me.

333
00:26:30,340 --> 00:26:33,730
Please eat some more. Here.

334
00:26:33,730 --> 00:26:37,750
Eat some more meat.

335
00:26:48,060 --> 00:26:51,220
I peeled some pears.

336
00:26:51,260 --> 00:26:53,700
There is date ginger tea in the thermal too.

337
00:26:53,700 --> 00:26:56,660
Drink it slowly.

338
00:26:56,660 --> 00:26:59,590
Okay, thank you.

339
00:26:59,590 --> 00:27:05,630
I've made some salad and rice in the fridge, so have some when you get hungry.

340
00:27:05,630 --> 00:27:10,770
Please eat well. So you can get through this.

341
00:27:10,780 --> 00:27:13,930
I will get going now.

342
00:27:13,930 --> 00:27:17,440
Okay, I will eat well.

343
00:27:17,440 --> 00:27:21,080
Can we see each other again?

344
00:27:22,580 --> 00:27:26,810
Yes. I'll come by again.

345
00:27:26,810 --> 00:27:29,930
Okay. Bye--

346
00:27:34,000 --> 00:27:37,940
Oh, no!

347
00:27:37,950 --> 00:27:41,110
What do we do?

348
00:27:41,110 --> 00:27:44,720
Are you okay? What do we do?

349
00:27:44,720 --> 00:27:47,210
What should I do?

350
00:29:15,120 --> 00:29:18,930
Where did he go in the middle of the night?

351
00:30:12,890 --> 00:30:17,450
It's been a long time since you made old squash soup. It looks delicious.

352
00:30:17,450 --> 00:30:23,740
Yes, Mom. You can eat together when Se Ryun gets up.

353
00:30:23,740 --> 00:30:27,750
By the way, I didn't see Dan Dan when I got up.

354
00:30:27,750 --> 00:30:30,180
I don't think she came home last night.

355
00:30:30,180 --> 00:30:34,010
She texted me to say she would sleepover at a friend's house.

356
00:30:34,010 --> 00:30:36,100
Is that right?

357
00:30:36,100 --> 00:30:37,620
I will get going.

358
00:30:37,620 --> 00:30:42,220
Where are you taking this?

359
00:30:42,220 --> 00:30:45,030
I thought I would take it to her.

360
00:30:45,030 --> 00:30:46,850
What did you say?

361
00:30:46,850 --> 00:30:51,990
- Are you bring it to Anna Kim?
- Yes.

362
00:30:51,990 --> 00:30:59,950
I'm going there to say have this, get surgery well, and please live healthily.

363
00:30:59,950 --> 00:31:04,880
If she dies like that, Soo Chul will never forgive me.

364
00:31:04,880 --> 00:31:07,530
Same with Dan Dan.

365
00:31:07,530 --> 00:31:10,140
Yes, you've thought it right.

366
00:31:10,140 --> 00:31:13,850
You have to save people first.

367
00:31:13,850 --> 00:31:18,090
And there is never a downside to doing good.

368
00:31:18,090 --> 00:31:21,620
All of it will come back as a fortune.

369
00:31:21,620 --> 00:31:26,090
Soo Chul will be grateful to you for the rest of his life too.

370
00:31:26,090 --> 00:31:28,270
Please get going.

371
00:31:28,290 --> 00:31:30,560
Okay.

372
00:31:35,630 --> 00:31:38,690
My poor daughter.

373
00:31:38,690 --> 00:31:43,750
Now she's taking care of her husband's sick ex-wife, who abandoned their daughter.

374
00:31:43,750 --> 00:31:47,840
It's making me upset.

375
00:31:56,920 --> 00:31:58,750
Dan Dan!

376
00:31:58,750 --> 00:32:01,110
Mom...

377
00:32:13,200 --> 00:32:15,510
Why are you here?

378
00:32:15,510 --> 00:32:19,200
You told me you were sleeping at a friend's house yesterday, didn't you?

379
00:32:19,200 --> 00:32:21,910
Did you sleep here? In this house?

380
00:32:21,910 --> 00:32:24,490
Is this place your friend's house?!

381
00:32:24,490 --> 00:32:27,130
Mom, that is, that is...

382
00:32:27,130 --> 00:32:29,120
Were you taking care of your mother here?

383
00:32:29,120 --> 00:32:30,630
Instead of your dad?

384
00:32:30,630 --> 00:32:32,800
Did your dad ask you to do this?

385
00:32:32,800 --> 00:32:36,690
No, Mom. I did it alone. Dad doesn't know anything.

386
00:32:36,690 --> 00:32:40,230
Yesterday, CEO Anna was very sick, that's why.

387
00:32:40,230 --> 00:32:41,670
I am sorry.

388
00:32:41,670 --> 00:32:43,730
I should've not let Dan Dan sleep over here.

389
00:32:43,730 --> 00:32:48,880
I should have sent her to go home, but everything was my fault.

390
00:32:48,880 --> 00:32:51,480
You shouldn't do this.

391
00:32:51,480 --> 00:32:54,020
Was it not enough for you to take my husband away from me?

392
00:32:54,020 --> 00:32:56,890
Are you even trying to steal Dan Dan from me?

393
00:32:56,890 --> 00:33:00,030
Don't you think you are going overboard?

394
00:33:00,050 --> 00:33:02,060
I'm really sorry.

395
00:33:02,060 --> 00:33:04,140
Dan Dan, please go. Go with your mom.

396
00:33:04,140 --> 00:33:06,510
Dan Dan, you.

397
00:33:06,520 --> 00:33:08,620
You don't have to come home now.

398
00:33:08,620 --> 00:33:12,150
Live here from now on with your mom!

399
00:33:13,470 --> 00:33:15,270
Mom! Mom!

400
00:33:15,270 --> 00:33:18,840
Dan Dan, go. Go follow her.

401
00:33:23,640 --> 00:33:28,010
I should have sent her back earlier, but what did I do again?

402
00:33:28,010 --> 00:33:31,540
Am I being greedy again? Am I?

403
00:33:36,240 --> 00:33:39,790
Mom, I am sorry. I am really sorry.

404
00:33:39,790 --> 00:33:42,790
I lied to you about sleeping at my friend's house.

405
00:33:42,790 --> 00:33:45,920
You said you'd take my side.

406
00:33:45,920 --> 00:33:51,690
So I thought at least you would understand me.

407
00:33:51,690 --> 00:33:55,280
But how can you do this to me too?

408
00:33:55,280 --> 00:33:58,630
You even lied to me that you'd be sleeping at your friend's house.

409
00:33:58,630 --> 00:34:02,340
If you told me you wanted to come here, did you think I'd prevent you from coming?

410
00:34:02,340 --> 00:34:04,720
I...

411
00:34:04,720 --> 00:34:07,130
I feel like I got betrayed.

412
00:34:07,130 --> 00:34:11,350
How could you even do this to me?

413
00:34:11,350 --> 00:34:15,350
Mom, I am very sorry. I was wrong.

414
00:34:15,350 --> 00:34:20,240
Yesterday, CEO Anna was throwing up and very sick, so I couldn't leave her alone.

415
00:34:20,240 --> 00:34:23,540
If I told you the truth, I thought you would be sad and upset.

416
00:34:23,540 --> 00:34:29,430
So I lied that I'd sleep at a friend's house. Mom, I'm really sorry.

417
00:34:29,450 --> 00:34:34,100
I really hate CEO Anna, but...

418
00:34:34,110 --> 00:34:38,770
I also pity her.

419
00:34:38,770 --> 00:34:41,770
Mom, I am very sorry, but...

420
00:34:41,770 --> 00:34:48,290
Can you understand me just once?

421
00:34:51,370 --> 00:34:54,120
Let me go.

422
00:34:56,700 --> 00:34:58,620
Mom...

423
00:34:58,620 --> 00:35:01,590
Mom!

424
00:35:13,440 --> 00:35:16,190
Yeon Sil.

425
00:35:16,190 --> 00:35:21,280
Please forgive me once.

426
00:35:24,710 --> 00:35:30,900
Let me go to her.

427
00:35:30,900 --> 00:35:34,400
While she's getting her surgery,

428
00:35:34,400 --> 00:35:40,810
please allow me to be with her. Please.

429
00:35:40,820 --> 00:35:43,640
I beg you.

430
00:35:49,740 --> 00:35:55,140
I really hate CEO Anna, but I also pity her.

431
00:35:55,140 --> 00:35:58,140
Mom, I am very sorry, but...

432
00:35:58,140 --> 00:36:02,670
Can you understand me just once?

433
00:36:30,760 --> 00:36:33,090
Are you back now?

434
00:36:33,090 --> 00:36:35,620
- Are you okay?
- Yes.

435
00:36:35,620 --> 00:36:37,990
Mom, you are back.

436
00:36:42,220 --> 00:36:46,490
You can go. Go and save that woman.

437
00:36:46,490 --> 00:36:49,930
Your body is here, but your mind is there right now.

438
00:36:49,930 --> 00:36:51,740
You are only worried about that woman.

439
00:36:51,740 --> 00:36:56,970
So don't pretend to work and go.

440
00:36:56,970 --> 00:37:01,800
Honey, I'm not.

441
00:37:01,800 --> 00:37:04,940
Why are you saying that?

442
00:37:04,940 --> 00:37:07,040
That woman is Dan Dan's mom.

443
00:37:07,040 --> 00:37:11,410
That's why I wanted to save her for Dan Dan's sake. I don't have any other intentions.

444
00:37:11,410 --> 00:37:13,900
So please don't waste your time and go.

445
00:37:13,900 --> 00:37:17,930
Go and do whatever you can to save her.

446
00:37:17,930 --> 00:37:22,350
That way, you won't resent me later.

447
00:37:22,400 --> 00:37:24,970
When you feel comfortable,

448
00:37:24,970 --> 00:37:27,220
I would feel at ease as well.

449
00:37:27,220 --> 00:37:30,860
So please go.

450
00:37:33,110 --> 00:37:35,460
Honey.

451
00:37:36,960 --> 00:37:42,260
Thank you, really thank you.

452
00:37:50,260 --> 00:37:55,660
That bad guy... How can you really go even I say so?

453
00:37:55,660 --> 00:37:59,740
How can you go without looking back at me?

454
00:38:21,120 --> 00:38:24,350
Yes, Dan Dan's mother.

455
00:38:24,350 --> 00:38:26,940
CEO Anna.

456
00:38:26,940 --> 00:38:30,300
My husband will go there.

457
00:38:30,300 --> 00:38:33,010
I gave him permission to go.

458
00:38:33,010 --> 00:38:35,490
So ask him to do anything you need.

459
00:38:35,490 --> 00:38:39,150
Please get surgery and stay alive,

460
00:38:39,150 --> 00:38:42,670
and I hope you'll recover soon.

461
00:38:42,670 --> 00:38:46,050
That way, I'd feel at ease.

462
00:38:48,630 --> 00:38:52,350
Dan Dan's mother, Dan Dan's mother!!

463
00:38:56,230 --> 00:39:00,670
What is going on right now?

464
00:39:00,670 --> 00:39:05,550
Ji Young, Ji Young!

465
00:39:05,550 --> 00:39:09,440
Soo Chul, why did you come here again?

466
00:39:09,440 --> 00:39:12,250
I told you not to come back.

467
00:39:12,250 --> 00:39:14,900
My wife permitted me.

468
00:39:14,900 --> 00:39:20,640
Until you get the surgery and get better, I'll stay by your side.

469
00:39:20,650 --> 00:39:25,640
Soo Chul, how could you come here even though your wife told you to come?

470
00:39:25,640 --> 00:39:28,100
Do you think you are helping me by doing this?

471
00:39:28,100 --> 00:39:30,390
Do you think it's for me?

472
00:39:30,390 --> 00:39:32,240
It's not.

473
00:39:32,240 --> 00:39:34,740
It makes me more exhausting,

474
00:39:34,740 --> 00:39:37,920
and it makes my life harder.

475
00:39:37,920 --> 00:39:42,250
You are making me into a worse person.

476
00:39:42,250 --> 00:39:44,220
Ji Young.

477
00:39:44,220 --> 00:39:48,090
So please, Soo Chul.

478
00:39:48,090 --> 00:39:53,690
Please don't come here again. I don't want to hurt your wife anymore.

479
00:39:53,730 --> 00:39:57,520
- Ji Young.
- All the wrongs I did until now are more than enough.

480
00:39:57,520 --> 00:39:59,630
I don't want to do that again.

481
00:39:59,630 --> 00:40:03,550
So please go home, Soo Chul. Right now. I beg you.

482
00:40:03,550 --> 00:40:06,430
You are not helping me by doing this!

483
00:40:06,430 --> 00:40:08,470
How can you do it alone?

484
00:40:08,470 --> 00:40:14,860
How can you handle that big surgery? Let me stay by your side until you finish the surgery.

485
00:40:14,860 --> 00:40:17,500
Soo Chul.

486
00:40:17,500 --> 00:40:24,720
If you insist on acting like this, I'll really disappear and die at the place where there's nobody.

487
00:40:24,720 --> 00:40:29,590
I mean it. I won't get the surgery as well.

488
00:40:31,490 --> 00:40:34,570
I get it.

489
00:40:34,570 --> 00:40:36,830
I understand.

490
00:40:38,330 --> 00:40:42,460
I understand what you are saying.

491
00:40:42,460 --> 00:40:46,040
So please don't disappear and stay here.

492
00:40:46,040 --> 00:40:49,080
Stay here and get the surgery.

493
00:40:50,990 --> 00:40:56,720
I hope you can get through this on your own.

494
00:41:07,620 --> 00:41:14,630
I came to apologize. I'm truly sorry.

495
00:41:14,660 --> 00:41:17,350
I should be punished to death.

496
00:41:17,350 --> 00:41:19,740
Why are you doing this?

497
00:41:19,740 --> 00:41:22,560
I told you to use my husband.

498
00:41:22,560 --> 00:41:26,080
I mean it, but why are you saying no?

499
00:41:26,080 --> 00:41:28,680
Isn't that what you wanted?

500
00:41:28,680 --> 00:41:33,490
No, it's not. Really.

501
00:41:33,510 --> 00:41:40,110
It's true that I had bad intentions before.

502
00:41:40,110 --> 00:41:42,470
I knew it was wrong,

503
00:41:42,470 --> 00:41:48,520
but I tried to take Soo Chul and Dan Dan to America by luring them with money.

504
00:41:48,520 --> 00:41:53,190
I guess that's why...

505
00:41:53,190 --> 00:41:57,150
I'm being punished now.

506
00:42:00,350 --> 00:42:04,410
Don't worry about Soo Chul and Dan Dan.

507
00:42:04,410 --> 00:42:10,110
I'll go to America, and nobody will know about it.

508
00:42:10,110 --> 00:42:13,330
I'll disappear quietly.

509
00:42:15,060 --> 00:42:17,800
I'm truly sorry.

510
00:42:17,800 --> 00:42:19,580
What did you say?

511
00:42:19,580 --> 00:42:21,820
You're going to America?

512
00:42:21,820 --> 00:42:25,090
And you'll disappear quietly?

513
00:42:25,090 --> 00:42:27,420
I can't believe this.

514
00:42:27,420 --> 00:42:30,880
How could you be so selfish until the very end?

515
00:42:30,880 --> 00:42:35,760
Did you ever think how others would feel if you disappeared in that condition?

516
00:42:35,760 --> 00:42:38,690
What about me? Did you think about it?

517
00:42:38,690 --> 00:42:41,290
Are you trying to peg me as the bad person?

518
00:42:41,290 --> 00:42:44,640
No, I'm not doing that at all.

519
00:42:44,640 --> 00:42:48,960
It's because I've done too many wrongs to you.

520
00:42:48,980 --> 00:42:53,530
Then what should I do?

521
00:42:53,530 --> 00:42:59,490
Please tell me what you want. I'll do whatever you say so.

522
00:43:05,840 --> 00:43:08,340
Get the surgery.

523
00:43:08,340 --> 00:43:12,660
Become healthy and then go to America.

524
00:43:12,660 --> 00:43:16,760
That's what everyone wants from you.

525
00:43:16,760 --> 00:43:20,450
So don't think you're doing everyone a favor by disappearing.

526
00:43:20,450 --> 00:43:24,650
Don't tantalize people by doing that.

527
00:43:27,760 --> 00:43:30,630
I'm sorry.

528
00:43:34,750 --> 00:43:38,030
I'm truly sorry.

529
00:43:40,200 --> 00:43:47,880
I will never forget your graciousness and the gratitude I feel even after I die.

530
00:43:58,410 --> 00:44:05,840
Thank you so much for raising Dan Dan so well.

531
00:44:05,840 --> 00:44:08,610
